This is a node.js package. Note this use to come with the files nessary to run but this is just the barebones packages.

Install script

cd
npm install librepod
cd node_modules/librepod
sudo npm link

mkdir newProject
cd newProject
librepod init
librepod


or with LibrepodPlus
https://github.com/diltarget/LibrepodPlus

cd
npm install librepod
cd node_modules/librepod
sudo npm link

mkdir LibrepodLibs
cd LibrepodLibs
git clone https://github.com/diltarget/LibrepodPlus.git

cd
mkdir newProject
cd newProject
librepod init LibrepodPlus
librepod

open your web browser to localhost:8000/?object=math&call=add&a=60&b=12
